-- German ESM ruling important step for stable euro: Austria
-- 
-- Wed Sep 12, 2012 5:35am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/09/12/us-germany-court-austria-idUSBRE88B0FH20120912

 

 VIENNA  (Reuters) - Austrian Chancellor Werner Faymann hailed a German constitutional court ruling on Wednesday allowing ratification of the euro zone's ESM permanent bailout fund as "an important step for the stability of the euro and essential for the future of Europe". 
 (Reporting by  Michael Shields ; Editing by Toby Chopra)